sd=Customer Case Management	Track and assess case load and resolution activity - allocate resources as necessary to optimize case resolution performance	Customer case handling is assessed over a period and the rules and thresholds guiding resolution decisions recalibrated	Manage customer case handling, track the effectiveness and impact of case resolution. Evaluate and confirm that the decision making rules and thresholds are well balanced in terms of equitable determination with general customer and merchant acceptance of the process. Ensure and that sufficient and appropriately trained resources are available
sdpath=customer-case-management
crpath=customer-case-management-plan
crr=Customer Case Management Plan Instance
mcr=Customer Case Management Plan
bqs=Rules Performance
